com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6a588950-c868-4923-a25c-5df62649205f_1160x424.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6a588950-c868-4923-a25c-5df62649205f_1160x424.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6a588950-c868-4923-a25c-5df62649205f_1160x424.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6a588950-c868-4923-a25c-5df62649205f_1160x424.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6a588950-c868-4923-a25c-5df62649205f_1160x424.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6a588950-c868-4923-a25c-5df62649205f_1160x424.png" width="1160" height="424" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/6a588950-c868-4923-a25c-5df62649205f_1160x424.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:424,&quot;width&quot;:1160,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:32853,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6a588950-c868-4923-a25c-5df62649205f_1160x424.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6a588950-c868-4923-a25c-5df62649205f_1160x424.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6a588950-c868-4923-a25c-5df62649205f_1160x424.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F6a588950-c868-4923-a25c-5df62649205f_1160x424.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p><a href="https://x.com/jsngr/status/1838396689708638367">Link to Post</a></p><p>I‚Äôve been talking for a while now about how we‚Äôre going to see dynamically-created personalized software in the near future, where you can ask your hardware devices to build new software for you on-demand, just when you need it.</p><p>A fun step in that direction, that‚Äôs extremely generalizable and potentially a venture-scale opportunity is a platform that allows users to create a UI simply by providing:</p><ol><li><p>A dataset (or even just a schema ‚Äî the platform could pull in data from the internet in some cases)</p></li><li><p>A prompt giving it some level of direction on the UI and UX</p></li></ol><p>Imagine the ability of turning any and every Google Sheet you use into a customizable UI in seconds.</p><p>I actually love this idea. If you‚Äôre technical and thinking about exploring it, let me know ‚Äî we should chat.</p><h3>üß†<strong> Framework: Marc Andreessen‚Äôs Hiring Advice</strong></h3><p>Once you‚Äôve hired a lot of people you probably have developed your own style to find the things <em>you</em> value.</p><p>But many founders don‚Äôt really know what they‚Äôre doing when they hire for the first time, across various types of rolls.</p><p>Here‚Äôs a TLDR from Marc Andreessen:</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff82f30f4-1010-4886-8cac-2a6c7126eaab_820x1008.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff82f30f4-1010-4886-8cac-2a6c7126eaab_820x1008.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff82f30f4-1010-4886-8cac-2a6c7126eaab_820x1008.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff82f30f4-1010-4886-8cac-2a6c7126eaab_820x1008.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff82f30f4-1010-4886-8cac-2a6c7126eaab_820x1008.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff82f30f4-1010-4886-8cac-2a6c7126eaab_820x1008.png" width="820" height="1008" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f82f30f4-1010-4886-8cac-2a6c7126eaab_820x1008.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1008,&quot;width&quot;:820,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:169352,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff82f30f4-1010-4886-8cac-2a6c7126eaab_820x1008.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff82f30f4-1010-4886-8cac-2a6c7126eaab_820x1008.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff82f30f4-1010-4886-8cac-2a6c7126eaab_820x1008.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff82f30f4-1010-4886-8cac-2a6c7126eaab_820x1008.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><h3><strong>üõ† Tool: <a href="https://www.particl.com/reports/content/bfcm-2024?utm_source=social&amp;utm_medium=Ad&amp;utm_campaign=Houck">Particl</a></strong></h3><p>Tired of guessing what are the best strategies for Black Friday &amp; Cyber Monday? Use <a href="https://www.particl.com/reports/content/bfcm-2024?utm_source=social&amp;utm_medium=Ad&amp;utm_campaign=Houck">Particl‚Äôs e-commerce database</a> to look back on BFCM 2021, 2022, and 2023 in order to forecast 2024.</p><p>We take a deep-dive into:</p><ul><li><p>When does BFCM start?</p></li><li><p>What discounting strategies are most effective?</p></li><li><p>What are the top trends heading into BFCM 2024?</p></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.particl.com/reports/content/bfcm-2024?utm_source=social&amp;utm_medium=Ad&amp;utm_campaign=Houck">Download our free 2024 e-commerce trends guide</a>&nbsp;to gain crucial insights as you gear up for Black Friday and Cyber Monday.*</p><h3>üìà<strong> Trend: Taste</strong></h3><p>The opportunity of the week, from above, is in line with the broader trend of software not being a differentiator any more.</p><p>You may have read <a href="https://www.workingtheorys.com/p/taste-is-eating-silicon-valley">this excellent essay</a> on why taste, and opinionated software, is now a bigger differentiator than the software itself‚Ä¶ or, at least, that‚Äôs where we‚Äôre heading.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c94d8c0-9145-4272-8b91-26f549f05a6f_1164x856.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c94d8c0-9145-4272-8b91-26f549f05a6f_1164x856.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c94d8c0-9145-4272-8b91-26f549f05a6f_1164x856.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c94d8c0-9145-4272-8b91-26f549f05a6f_1164x856.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c94d8c0-9145-4272-8b91-26f549f05a6f_1164x856.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c94d8c0-9145-4272-8b91-26f549f05a6f_1164x856.png" width="1164" height="856" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1c94d8c0-9145-4272-8b91-26f549f05a6f_1164x856.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:856,&quot;width&quot;:1164,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:195117,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c94d8c0-9145-4272-8b91-26f549f05a6f_1164x856.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c94d8c0-9145-4272-8b91-26f549f05a6f_1164x856.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c94d8c0-9145-4272-8b91-26f549f05a6f_1164x856.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1c94d8c0-9145-4272-8b91-26f549f05a6f_1164x856.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p><a href="https://x.com/anuatluru/status/1836875352347398413">Link to Post</a></p><p>If you‚Äôre looking to start new, venture-scale ideas I‚Äôd look for things outside of traditional SaaS:</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcb92eb43-f482-4bfd-940b-46cf796bc7ca_351x501.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcb92eb43-f482-4bfd-940b-46cf796bc7ca_351x501.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcb92eb43-f482-4bfd-940b-46cf796bc7ca_351x501.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcb92eb43-f482-4bfd-940b-46cf796bc7ca_351x501.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcb92eb43-f482-4bfd-940b-46cf796bc7ca_351x501.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcb92eb43-f482-4bfd-940b-46cf796bc7ca_351x501.png" width="535" height="763.6324786324786" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/cb92eb43-f482-4bfd-940b-46cf796bc7ca_351x501.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:501,&quot;width&quot;:351,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:535,&quot;bytes&quot;:115202,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcb92eb43-f482-4bfd-940b-46cf796bc7ca_351x501.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcb92eb43-f482-4bfd-940b-46cf796bc7ca_351x501.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcb92eb43-f482-4bfd-940b-46cf796bc7ca_351x501.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fcb92eb43-f482-4bfd-940b-46cf796bc7ca_351x501.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><h3>üí¨<strong> Quote: First Draft Speed</strong></h3><p>You don‚Äôt need to get it right.</p><p>You really don‚Äôt.</p><p>But you do set the pace of the company as the founder.</p><p>If you take a day to respond to your team‚Äôs messages, or put together a draft of something, they certainly won‚Äôt put in the extra effort to be fast either.</p><p>The best founders I know get things down on paper and start moving as fast as possible. They ship quickly and get in front of customers quickly.</p><p>That‚Äôs why I like this idea of ‚Äúfirst draft speed‚Äù from Shaan Puri.</p><p>If VCs were easily able to measure this when considering making an investment, I believe we‚Äôd have a much higher hit rate in the industry.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05acc85a-a505-4257-b662-2b2eb6c33adf_1166x494.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-