line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>B≈´t≈≥ malonu, jei komentaruose papasakotumƒót, koki≈≥ tribute‚Äô≈≥ esat matƒô, gal juos apgintumƒót, pagrƒØstumƒót j≈≥ prasmƒô. </p><div><hr></div><blockquote><h4>U≈æsienio naujienos</h4></blockquote><ul><li><p><strong>A$AP Rocky</strong> i≈°leido Kijive nufilmuotƒÖ ir su ukrainieƒçi≈≥ komanda kurtƒÖ klipƒÖ ‚ÄûTailor Swif‚Äú. Klipas nufilmuotas 2021 m. gruodƒØ. Vaizdo klipai retai man b≈´na ƒØdom≈´s, bet ≈°itƒÖ farsƒÖ chru≈°ƒçiovki≈≥ kiemuose ≈æi≈´rƒóƒçiau ir ≈æi≈´rƒóƒçiau. Gaila, kad tai ne Vilniaus reklama.</p><div id="youtube2-5URefVYaJrA" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;5URefVYaJrA&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:&quot;8s&quot;,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/5URefVYaJrA?start=8s&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div></li><li><p>Ka≈ækada neseniai su ≈æmona i≈°siskyrƒó Noelis Gallagheris. Tad i≈°mokƒójus kompensacijƒÖ ir sƒÖskaitoje pastebimai suma≈æƒójus pinig≈≥, dabar milijonas britpopo gerbƒój≈≥ raunasi plaukus mƒógindami gauti bilietƒÖ ƒØ <strong>Oasis </strong>atsik≈´rimo koncertus. La≈æyb≈≥ bendrovƒóse taip pat galima statyti u≈æ tai, ar grupƒó vƒól nei≈°siskirs iki turo prad≈æios ir ar i≈°temps visus suplanuotus koncertus. Kaip galit suprast i≈° mano tono, stati≈°kas Oasis rokas manƒôs nejaudina ‚Äì nors Liamo karkimas visai mielas. Mƒógau tik The Verve su tuo bittersweet klipu, kur ≈æingsniuodamas biƒças dau≈æosi ƒØ praeivius. </p></li><li><p><strong>Taylor Swift</strong> nusifotkino su kaƒçiuku. Ir i≈°kart po prezidentini≈≥ debat≈≥ i≈°rei≈°kƒó paramƒÖ Kamalai. Ar kaƒçiukas privilios balsuoti jauniausius amerikieƒçius? Ar padƒós ƒØveikti oran≈æinƒØ nemirtingƒÖjƒØ Ko≈°ƒçƒój≈≥? </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10922ad1-17ec-4d96-8302-fb609538bae4_645x809.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10922ad1-17ec-4d96-8302-fb609538bae4_645x809.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10922ad1-17ec-4d96-8302-fb609538bae4_645x809.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10922ad1-17ec-4d96-8302-fb609538bae4_645x809.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10922ad1-17ec-4d96-8302-fb609538bae4_645x809.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10922ad1-17ec-4d96-8302-fb609538bae4_645x809.png" width="263" height="329.8713178294574" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/10922ad1-17ec-4d96-8302-fb609538bae4_645x809.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:809,&quot;width&quot;:645,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:263,&quot;bytes&quot;:729387,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&qu