er"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/aC4BC-Hxq9g?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><p>Man asmeni≈°kai Puff Daddy visad pirmiausia buvo Jennifer Lopez biƒças ir dar ≈°ito ƒØsp≈´dingo mashupo su Led Zeppelin≈≥ ‚ÄûKashmir‚Äú autorius. Bet jei galvojat, kad jis seniai pamir≈°tas ir nebesvarbus, tai ≈æinokit, kad 2022 m. jo turtas ƒØvertintas milijardu doleri≈≥, jis yra antras turtingiausias reperis po Jay Z (babkes jam krauna vodkos, drabu≈æi≈≥, kvepal≈≥, televizijos, ≈æaidim≈≥ investicijos). Dabar gi i≈° jo atimtas garbƒós laipsnis Howardo universitete ir simbolinis Niujorko raktas.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cb9a795-bbc0-4921-850a-4e6f87363633_813x572.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cb9a795-bbc0-4921-850a-4e6f87363633_813x572.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cb9a795-bbc0-4921-850a-4e6f87363633_813x572.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5cb9a795-bbc0-4921-850a-4e6f87363633_813x572.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.c