e-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Ai≈°ku, ≈°iuo metu dreba tikrai ne vienas ≈°ou verslo atstovas, nes ≈æadama atskleisti daugiau ‚Äûdideli≈≥ vard≈≥‚Äú, mielai dalyvavusi≈≥ pagarsƒójusiuose Diddy vakarƒóliuose ‚Äì Freak Offs. Pasak advokato, ≈°itie parƒçiai ir afterparƒçiai vykdavo albumo i≈°leidimo, Naujako, Liepos 4osios proga, taip pat ‚Äûpuppy parties‚Äú, ‚Äûall white parties‚Äú... Ten vykdavo sekso ≈°ou tarp sekso darbuotoj≈≥ ir, galimai, apsvaigint≈≥ dalyvi≈≥. Vakarƒóli≈≥ sƒÖra≈°uose yra Ashton Kutcher, Jennifer Lopez, Will Smith, Sarah Jessica Parker, Leonardo DiCaprio, Beyonc√©, Khloe Kardashian.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff061ea6a-9479-4da6-b210-77e9cab1655d_703x707.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff061ea6a-9479-4da6-b210-77e9cab1655d_703x707.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff061ea6a-9479-4da6-b210-77e9cab1655d_703x707.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff061ea6a-9479-4da6-b210-77e9cab1655d_703x707.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_