112	https://thefoundingjourney.substack.com/p/how-steven-galanis-grew-cameo-into	How Steven Galanis Grew Cameo Into a $1 Billion Unicorn 	Our second episode for the Founding Journey podcast!	<html><head></head><body><p>Each Thursday I‚Äôll interview a world-class founder about their unique paths to uncover tactical insights they've learned about how to fundraise, grow, validate, hire, scale, and lead teams.</p><p>The first <em>two</em> episodes are live right now, including this conversation with Steven Galanis from Cameo.</p><p>Steven is the co-founder and CEO of Cameo. He grew the company from 0 into a $1 billion unicorn pursued by every top VC firm. Millions of Cameos have been sent since the company was founded and they recently raised fresh capital after a few rounds of layoffs. Steven was open and candid with me about that journey.</p><p>If you prefer, you can watch on <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@foundingjourney?sub_confirmation=1">YouTube</a> or listen on <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/4SqCLo3ruK3MGCIoJvPdbR?si=f5157619cac74722">Spotify</a>, <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/ng/podcast/founding-journey/id1773179683">Apple</a> or your podcast platform of choice.</p><div id="youtube2-uyYdcyFLURE" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;uyYdcyFLURE&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:&quot;1s&quot;,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/uyYdcyFLURE?start=1s&amp;rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div><p>In the episode, we discuss:</p><p><strong>The Journey to Cameo</strong></p><ul><li><p>(01:33) ‚Äî&nbsp; Steven's 1st business: Spartan Entertainment</p></li><li><p>(04:26) ‚Äî Steven's pre-Cameo work experience</p></li><li><p>(06:33) ‚Äî Starting Cameo with