w.linkedin.com/in/victoria-toli/">Victoria Toli</a>, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/theodore-janson/">Theodore Janson</a></p></li><li><p><strong>Signal: </strong>Finny has rapidly expanded its team in the fall and is seeing solid growth in website visitors and social media following</p></li></ul><div><hr></div><h2>Growth Startups üöÄ</h2><h4><strong><a href="https://www.legalfly.ai">LEGALFLY</a> üá¨üáß</strong></h4><ul><li><p><strong>Industry:</strong> LegalTech</p></li><li><p><strong>What they do:</strong> LegalFly offers a secure AI platform for legal teams, specializing in contract review, drafting, and discovery, leveraging AI technology to streamline document analysis and reduce review time while prioritizing privacy and security through anonymization. The platform also allows for the creation of specialized Legal AI copilots for training and analysis of unstructured documents.</p></li><li><p><strong>Last Funding:</strong> Series A</p></li><li><p><strong>Total Funding: </strong>18‚Äô560‚Äô508 USD</p></li><li><p><strong>Notable Investors:</strong> <a href="https://www.notion.vc">Notion Capital</a>, <a href="http://redalpine">redalpine</a>, <a href="https://www.fortinocapital.com">Fortino Capital</a>, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mghissassi/">Mehdi Ghissassi</a></p></li><li><p><strong>Team: </strong><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dennis-montegnies-42b58926/">Dennis Montegnies</a>, <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/rmiessen/">Ruben Miessen</a></p></li><li><p><strong>Signal: </strong>Legalfly added 11 people in the last 90 days and is hiring for 20 positions, LinkedIn followers more than doubled over the last 6 months</p></li></ul><h4><strong><a href="https://www.attotude.com">Atto Tude</a> üá∫üá∏</strong></h4><ul><li><p><strong>Industry: </strong>Data Centers</p></li><li><p><strong>What they do: </strong>AttoTude specializes in interconnect technology aimed at enhancing data center efficiency, particularly for artificial intelligence and supercomputing applications. This technology addresses networking limitations and facilitates high-speed parallel processing.</p></li><li><p><strong>Last Funding: </strong>Series A</p></li><li><p><strong>Total Funding:</strong> 40‚Äô168‚Äô034 USD</p></li><li><p><strong>Notable Investors: </strong><a href="https://shv.com">Sutter Hill Ventures</a>, <a href="https://www.canaan.com">Canaan</a>, <a href="https://www.wing.vc">Wing Venture Capital</a></p></li><li><p><strong>Team:</strong><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ianswanson/"> </a><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dave-welch-b359b630/">Dave Welch</a></p></li><li><p><strong>Signal: </strong>After a series-A led by Sutter Hill and Wing, AttoTude has money to spend, with funding per employee standing at $6.69M</p></li></ul><div><hr></div><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd775c953-c12b-4d00-8d3f-8f13d50677fd_480x270.gif" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd775c953-c12b-4d00-8d3f-8f13d50677fd_480x270.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd775c953-c12b-4d00-8d3f-8f13d50677fd_480x270.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd775c953-c12b-4d00-8d3f-8f13d50677fd_480x270.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_lossy/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd775c953-c12b-4