135	https://thefoundingjourney.substack.com/p/when-to-start-a-startup	When to Start a Startup	And why the definition of SaaS is flipping	<html><head></head><body><p>Hey y‚Äôall ‚Äî here‚Äôs today at a glance:</p><blockquote><p><strong>Opportunity ‚Üí</strong> Multiplayer AI App</p><p><strong>Framework ‚Üí</strong> When to Start a Startup</p><p><strong>Tool ‚Üí</strong> Global Benchmark Report</p><p><strong>Trend ‚Üí</strong> Service as a Software</p><p><strong>Quote ‚Üí</strong> The Collison Install</p></blockquote><p><em>PS ‚Äî <a href="https://houck.news/upgrade">Become a member</a> to get access to my founder membership including an engaged community, fundraising support, fireside chats and more.</em></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://thefoundingjourney.substack.com/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://thefoundingjourney.substack.com/subscribe?"><span>Subscribe now</span></a></p><div><hr></div><h3>üîó<strong> Houck‚Äôs Picks</strong></h3><p><em>My favorite finds of the week.</em></p><p><strong>Fundraising</strong></p><ul><li><p>An active early-stage fund looking to invest in startups (<a href="https://x.com/DarrelFrater/status/1839427028543742217">Link</a>)</p></li></ul><p><strong>Growth</strong></p><ul><li><p>Product launch checklist (<a href="https://x.com/lukemiler/status/1841850332520779776?s=42">Link</a>)</p></li><li><p>Mastering TikTok to get millions in ARR (<a href="https://x.com/blakeandersonw/status/1842349939088925146?s=42">Link</a>)</p></li><li><p>How to promote your startup with $0 (<a href="https://x.com/natiakourdadze/status/1841152672839450929?s=42">Link</a>)</p></li></ul><p><strong>ICYMI</strong></p><ul><li><p>Compare your DNA to 180,000+ founders worldwide and discover your strongest traits as a startup founder.&nbsp;<a href="https://fndri.com/4c2XvF3">Get your Entrepreneur DNA report here.</a>*</p></li><li><p>HubSpot‚Äôs co-founder‚Äôs biggest lessons (<a href="https://x.com/bhalligan/status/1841169106659119406">Link</a>)</p></li><li><p>Unexpected things this founder learned from the YC Alumni reunion (<a href="https://x.com/frantzfries/status/1842629959355081207">Link</a>)</p><div><hr></div></li></ul><h3>üí° <strong>Opportunity: Multiplayer AI App</strong></h3><p>It‚Äôs time for a new social app.</p><p>TikTok has matured, Meta‚Äôs products reek of last-gen energy, and no new breakouts have emerged yet despite AI‚Äôs emergence into the broader zeitgeist being almost 2 years old.</p><p>X is rising but is also fundamentally a last-gen product.</p><p>We‚Äôve seen novel single-player AI products like <a href="http://character.ai">character.ai</a>, but no breakout multiplayer experiences</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F527df704-f8dc-41d5-ad64-20b1577aa1cd_1160x542.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F527df704-f8dc-41d5-ad64-20b1577aa1cd_1160x542.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F527df704-f8dc-41d5-ad64-20b1577aa1cd_1160x542.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F527df704-f8dc-41d5-ad64-20b1577aa1cd_1160x542.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F527df704-f8dc-41d5-ad64-20b1577aa1cd_1160x542.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F527df704-f8dc-41d5-ad64-20b1577aa1cd_1160x542.png" width="1160" height="542" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/527df704-f8dc-41d5-ad64-20b1577aa1cd_1160x542.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:542,&quot;width&quot;:1160,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:37926,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F527df704-f8dc-41d5-ad64-20b1577aa1cd_1160x542.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F527df704-f8dc-41d5-ad64-20b1577aa1cd_1160x542.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F527df704-f8dc-41d5-ad64-20b1577aa1cd_1160x542.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F527df704-f8dc-41d5-ad64-20b1577aa1cd_1160x542.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p><a href="https://x.com/jmj/status/1841533090495381771">Link to Post</a></p><p>What is the easy-to-digest implementation of AI that will create new relationships and social experiences online?</p><ul><li><p>Facebook connected people</p></li><li><p>Instagram let them express themselves with photos</p></li><li><p>TikTok made creating engaging videos possible for anyone</p></li></ul><p>What‚Äôs next?</p><h3>üß†<strong> Framework: When to Start a Startup</strong></h3><p>No one wants to buy in at the top, but many founders actually do ‚Äî or at least closer to the top than they believe to be the case.</p><p>It surprised me when I realized that, but it‚Äôs true.</p><p>Too often people who want to start a startup will look for and base their decisions about what to build on the wrong signals.</p><p>Good signals usually come from potential customers.</p><p>Bad signals usually come from people talking about ‚Äúthe industry.‚Äù</p><p>The further removed someone is from the potential customers for a product, the less weight you should give their opinion on whether an opportunity is viable or not.</p><p>Here are some examples of when the consensus view was completely wrong</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1793490c-873c-4fe7-99b9-418171a3a484_986x988.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1793490c-873c-4fe7-99b9-418171a3a484_986x988.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1793490c-873c-4fe7-99b9-418171a3a484_986x988.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1793490c-873c-4fe7-99b9-418171a3a484_986x988.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1793490c-873c-4fe7-99b9-418171a3a484_986x988.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1793490c-873c-4fe7-99b9-418171a3a484_986x988.png" width="986" height="988" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1793490c-873c-4fe7-99b9-418171a3a484_986x988.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:988,&quot;width&quot;:986,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:192706,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1793490c-873c-4fe7-99b9-418171a3a484_986x988.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1793490c-873c-4fe7-99b9-418171a3a484_986x988.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1793490c-873c-4fe7-99b9-418171a3a484_986x988.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1793490c-873c-4fe7-99b9-418171a3a484_986x988.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>This doesn‚Äôt mean you shouldn‚Äôt seek advice about the things you yourself don‚Äôt understand. It just means you should be careful what parts and how much of that advice to accept as gospel.</p><p>Instead, operate from first principles.</p><h3><strong>üõ† Tool: Global Benchmark Report</strong></h3><p>The best product teams don‚Äôt iterate in a silo. They use benchmarks (for metrics like user retention, feature adoption, and stickiness) to compare, understand, and improve product performance.</p><p>Curious what KPIs you should be tracking and what ‚Äúgood‚Äù looks like? Find out in&nbsp;<a href="https://go.pendo.io/2024-global-product-benchmarks.html??utm_source=big_technology&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=houcks-newsletter&amp;utm_content=tool">Mind the Product‚Äôs global benchmarks report</a>. Powered by 6,800 applications using Pendo, it‚Äôs here to help you understand how you‚Äôre doing‚Äîand where to improve.</p><p><a href="https://go.pendo.io/2024-global-product-benchmarks.html??utm_source=big_technology&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_campaign=houcks-newsletter&amp;utm_content=tool">Benchmark your product</a> here.</p><h3>üìà<strong> Trend: AI Service as a Software</strong></h3><p>This trend probably needs a grammatically-correct name, but it‚Äôs becoming hard to deny.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd0c8f81-f9bc-4cf1-8a1e-4a80e60f383b_1166x492.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd0c8f81-f9bc-4cf1-8a1e-4a80e60f383b_1166x492.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd0c8f81-f9bc-4cf1-8a1e-4a80e60f383b_1166x492.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd0c8f81-f9bc-4cf1-8a1e-4a80e60f383b_1166x492.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd0c8f81-f9bc-4cf1-8a1e-4a80e60f383b_1166x492.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd0c8f81-f9bc-4cf1-8a1e-4a80e60f383b_1166x492.png" width="1166" height="492" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/fd0c8f81-f9bc-4cf1-8a1e-4a80e60f383b_1166x492.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:492,&quot;width&quot;:1166,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:39279,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd0c8f81-f9bc-4cf1-8a1e-4a80e60f383b_1166x492.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd0c8f81-f9bc-4cf1-8a1e-4a80e60f383b_1166x492.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd0c8f81-f9bc-4cf1-8a1e-4a80e60f383b_1166x492.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffd0c8f81-f9bc-4cf1-8a1e-4a80e60f383b_1166x492.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p><a href="https://x.com/jaltma/status/1841900280956518469">Link to Post</a></p><p>The benefit is clear ‚Äî in the past, performing these tasks required expenses and headcount to scale linearly with revenue, since traditional SaaS wasn‚Äôt able to process the information fast or accurately enough.</p><p>But LLMs change that.</p><p>I imagine the biggest companies in this space have already been founded, and we‚Äôll see them become giant in the next few years, but there are likely many, many niche opportunities where this playbook can be applied in B2B.</p><h3>üí¨<strong> Quote: The Collison Install</strong></h3><p>These days most software gets sold as a subscription or is priced based on usage. We all know that, and most founders like it because it means predictable revenue (and, often, higher LTV).</p><p>But it also means more work is required from you and your team.</p><p>Getting someone to purchase your product isn‚Äôt the only thing that matters ‚Äî you need to make sure they actually set it up, implement it, and use it.</p><p>Otherwise they‚Äôll simply stop paying you for it (or, in the case of usage-based pricing, won‚Äôt ever start). This reduces your acceptable CAC and makes it harder to invest in growth.</p><p>The Collison brothers, who founded Stripe, realized this early on and took a more hands-on approach to sales:</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3af5cf7-51a9-4267-a5d7-3390b2d00a0f_996x530.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3af5cf7-51a9-4267-a5d7-3390b2d00a0f_996x530.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3af5cf7-51a9-4267-a5d7-3390b2d00a0f_996x530.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3af5cf7-51a9-4267-a5d7-3390b2d00a0f_996x530.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3af5cf7-51a9-4267-a5d7-3390b2d00a0f_996x530.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3af5cf7-51a9-4267-a5d7-3390b2d00a0f_996x530.png" width="996" height="530" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e3af5cf7-51a9-4267-a5d7-3390b2d00a0f_996x530.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:530,&quot;width&quot;:996,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:157790,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3af5cf7-51a9-4267-a5d7-3390b2d00a0f_996x530.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3af5cf7-51a9-4267-a5d7-3390b2d00a0f_996x530.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3