6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><h2>‚úçÔ∏è Key takeaways</h2><ul><li><p>Dorothy transitioned from tech roles to angel investing to support overlooked founders.</p></li><li><p>Diversity in founders leads to novel solutions and market activation.</p></li><li><p>Investing in women's health revealed deep-rooted social dynamics affecting spending.</p></li><li><p>Angel investing can be a lever for social change and innovation.</p></li><li><p>Access to networks is a valuable asset in angel investing.</p></li><li><p>Investing reveals beliefs about the future and desired change.</p></li><li><p>Scientific rigor and relational competence are crucial traits in founders.</p></li><li><p>Traditional VC metrics often overlook high-potential founders.</p></li><li><p>Systemic change is needed in how venture capital operates.</p></li><li><p>Trusting one's instincts and judgments is vital in investing.</p></li></ul><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F10d284dd-b5e9-4acd-a2a0-8d1717ad80f4_700x40.