ps://lu.ma/portfolio-modelling-2">üåç </a><strong><a href="https://lu.ma/portfolio-modelling-2">Milan</a></strong><a href="https://lu.ma/portfolio-modelling-2"> üìÖ Tue, Oct 29 | 10:00 AM - 1:00 PM CET </a>| Lecturer: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/marc-penkala/">Marc Penkala</a></p><p><strong><a href="https://airtable.com/app3F8k6EuPFgP51d/pag8kxa7qUd8z3Z1F/form">Benchmarking Session for GPs &amp; LPs</a></strong><br>üìÖ TBD - preregistration open now | Lecturer: To be announced ü§´</p><p><em>Got ideas or requests for future topics to cover? Let us know <a href="https://airtable.com/app3F8k6EuPFgP51d/pagM7nbwiEqUsHlJM/form">here</a>.</em></p><div><hr></div><h3><strong>üóìÔ∏è The VC Conferences You Can‚Äôt Miss</strong></h3><p><em>There are some events that just have to be on the calendar. Here‚Äôs our list, hit us up if you‚Äôre going, we‚Äôd love to meet!</em></p><p><strong><a href="https://bit.ly/WVCESummit24">WVC:E Summit 2024</a></strong><a href="https://www.wvce.tech/tickets-1"> </a>| | üìÜ 7-8 October | üåç Paris, France</p><p><strong><a href="https://bit.ly/NorthStarGITEX24">North Star &amp; GITEX Global </a></strong>| üìÜ 14 - 18 October | üåç Dubai, UAE</p><p><strong><a href="https://bit.ly/InvestBravery24">Invest in Bravery</a></strong> | üìÜ 21th of October | üåç Kyiv, Ukraine</p><p><strong><a href="https://bit.ly/0100Milan24">0100 Conference Mediterranean</a></strong> | üìÜ 28 - 30 October | Milano, Italy</p><p><strong><a href="https://bit.ly/culttech24">culttech summit</a></strong> | üìÜ 5-6 November | Vienna, Austria</p><p><strong><a href="https://bit.ly/GoWest25">GoWest</a> </strong>| üìÜ 28 - 30 January 2025 | üåç Gothenburg, Sweden</p><p><strong><a href="https://bit.ly/GITEXEU25">GITEX Europe 2025</a></strong> | üìÜ 23 - 25 May 2025 | üåç Berlin, Germany</p><div><hr></div></body></html>	Salomon Aiach and Blaise Matuidi discuss their journey as angel investors and venture capitalists, the challenges of the consumer sector, and