156	https://www.eu.vc/p/decarbonization-consumer-sector-as	Decarbonization, consumer sector as the underdog in VC and more! 	Learn directly from Origins Fund, Regeneration.VC, Ascension VC and SeedBlink.	<html><head></head><body><p>Today's email is loaded with a bunch of nuggets. First, we have two full-featured deep dives for you (#infinity scroll):</p><ul><li><p><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/d0869f38-8565-42e7-b0ca-2a558412a9db">A discussion on why the consumer sector is the underdog in venture capital with Salomon &amp; Blaise from Origins Fund</a></p></li><li><p><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/ee69b360-f804-4c59-88dc-b591020bdf79">Cambridge Scientists Secure $5M from Leading Global Venture Capital Funds and Corporations to Transform Scope 3 Decarbonization</a> </p></li></ul><p>And then we‚Äôve some amazing new submissions on the community insights platform we wanna share with you:</p><ul><li><p><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/finding-the-right-partner-beyond">Finding the right partner beyond the VC dream</a></p></li><li><p><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/ascension-vcs-ai-investing-lens">Ascension VC's AI investing lens</a></p></li></ul><p><strong><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScMVLQavzcoiDIOve1tARRVo9vtvscWdtwwwl5O2rnDYNhQIg/viewform?usp=sf_link">To get featured, go here </a>üåü</strong></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_au