/p><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>Daniel compares finding the right investor to finding the perfect running shoe. It‚Äôs all about alignment with your company‚Äôs needs, vision, and stage. </p><p>VCs should feel like co-founders, providing 24/7 support, deep expertise, and talent networks. Founders: do your own due diligence on potential investors‚Äîtalk to their portfolio startups and focus on alignment beyond capital </p><p><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/how-to-spot-the-best-vc-fund-for">Read the article here.</a></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8