invest.com/blog/the-rise-of-moove-key-learnings-from-africas-mobility-fintech-pioneer">Speedinvest blog.</a></p><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>Moove‚Äôs approach includes transforming weaknesses‚Äîlike currency volatility‚Äîinto competitive advantages through early geographic expansion and creating a mutually beneficial dependency with Uber, leading to strategic investment. Their pivot from fintech offerings back to core vehicle financing exemplifies the power of adaptability.</p><p>Moove's founders have also mastered the art of keeping investors, employees, and the public engaged, driving both trust and brand visibility. Lessons here? Flexibility, proactive scaling, and relentless engagement.</p><p><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/the-rise-of-moove-key-learnings-from">Read the article here</a></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%