mages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><p><strong><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/cambridge-scientists-secure-5m-from">Cambridge scientists secure $5M from leading global venture capital funds and corporations to transform scope 3 decarbonization</a></strong></p><p>by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ponvalley/">Michael Smith</a>, General Partner of <a href="http://regeneration.vc/">Regeneration.VC</a>.</p><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>Neutreeno's $5M seed round, backed by Regeneration.VC, Closed Loop Partners, and Scania Invest aim to revolutionize Scope 3 decarbonization. With 90%+ emissions in company value chains, most firms struggle to meet net-zero goals due to data gaps and high costs. </p><p>Neutreeno‚Äôs tech cuts through these issues, enabling precise, cost-effective emission reductions across complex supply chains.</p><p><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/cambridge-scientists-secure-5m-from">Read the article here.</a></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-medi