6b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><p><strong><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/from-viral-videos-to-a-250b-empire">From viral videos to a $250B empire: the rise and future of the creator economy</a></strong><br>by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/laetitia-exertier/?originalSubdomain=uk">Laetitia Exertier</a>, Summer Intern at <a href="https://www.referencecap.com/">Reference Capital</a> | Originally published on üî• <a href="https://medium.com/@ReferenceCapital/reference-newsflash-bb1579e20803">Reference Newsflash.</a></p><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>The creator economy has grown into a $250B industry, projected to reach $450B by 2027. The sector‚Äôs rapid rise is fueled by Gen Z‚Äôs drive for authenticity and democratized content but faces challenges as investment cools and monetization issues remain. </p><p>Startups are now expected to offer robust off-platform monetization options to ensure creators‚Äô income stability while attracting top talent and managing rapid content turnover. As ‚Äúinfluencers‚Äù and digital creators continue to influence sectors from finance to news, the future hinges on regulatory support and platforms addressing critical needs.</p><p><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/from-viral-videos-to-a-250b-empire">Read the article here.</a></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp" width="700" height="40" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:40,&quot;width&quot;:700,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><p><strong><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/the-great-vc-reset">The great VC reset</a></strong><br>by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alokik-advani-019443/">Alokik Advani</a>, Managing Partner at <a href="https://fisv.com/">Fidelity International Strategic Ventures</a>. | Originally published on <a href="https://fisv.com/perspectives/the-great-vc-reset">Fidelity International Strategic Ventures</a>.</p><p><strong>Why it matters: </strong>The post-2021 funding bubble has burst, with over 50% of unicorns needing fresh capital this year. Advani argues that as cash runs dry, startups must shift focus from growth-at-all-costs to sustainable fundamentals like profitability and product-market fit. </p><p>Founders face tough choices, including taking down rounds to ensure realistic valuations and employee equity value. This ‚Äúreset‚Äù will weed out weaker players but should ultimately benefit resilient startups by attracting aligned, long-term investors. Expect a return to prudent valuations, cleaner terms, and patient capital as the VC ecosystem finds a new balance.</p><p><a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/the-great-vc-reset">Read the article here.</a></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png" width="750" height="40" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/d7ca142d-62d2-4955-b9b4-e6cb7fc0e5c3_750x40.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:40,&quot;width&quot;:750,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot