tg7hNw0lk9SWD-uHxfc6kBz-3fvVJvlrEq9JvJ7noWstEN9w40nvMIkXuca6hJLzOFP_XvCE9cD4b3-N9UgBeirnkqIX0szOkuov6DWFBJNiOOgdSBtrLBnS6eHoe8H2ya1XhEz6T4GjYf17JqTRwjpFbi_-BAAA__-R9HXH">Broadhaven Ventures</a>. | Originally published on <a href="https://altgoesmainstream.substack.com/p/ep-12-taking-the-pulse-of-private">Alt Goes Mainstream</a>.</p><div><hr></div><p>Welcome to the 12th episode of the Monthly Alts Pulse, a collaboration between iCapital x Alt Goes Mainstream.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff02ab068-dbee-4fcf-9985-55115dd9221e_1920x1080.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff02ab068-dbee-4fcf-9985-55115dd9221e_1920x1080.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff02ab068-dbee-4fcf-9985-55115dd9221e_1920x1080.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff02ab068-dbee-4fcf-9985-55115dd9221e_1920x1080.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff02ab068-dbee-4fcf-9985-55115dd9221e_1920x1080.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff02ab068-dbee-4fcf-9985-55115dd9221e_1920x1080.jpeg" width="1456" height="819" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f02ab068-dbee-4fcf-9985-55115dd9221e_1920x1080.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:819,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:null,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff02ab068-dbee-4fcf-9985-55115dd9221e_1920x1080.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff02ab068-dbee-4fcf-9985-55115dd9221e_1920x1080.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff02ab068-dbee-4fcf-9985-55115dd9221e_1920x1080.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff02ab068-dbee-4fcf-9985-55115dd9221e_1920x1080.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>This month‚Äôs episode features one of <a href="https://icapital.com/">iCapital</a>‚Äôs senior executives, <a href="https://icapital.com/about-us/eileen-duff/">Eileen Duff</a>, Managing Partner &amp; Chief Client Success Officer, and a private markets veteran who was Head of Alternative Investments, North America for Credit Suisse for a number of years. At iCapital, she oversees Investor Relations, Enterprise Integration, and Client Operations teams to optimize the client experience. Eileen has had a number of senior and instrumental roles at iCapital. She's also a member of iCapital's Operating Committee. She was previously Head of Fund Management &amp; Research for iCapital, where she was responsible for origination and development of new investment products and lifecycle management of existing offerings. She also led Distribution for iCapital, leading the sales and relationship management function after joining from Credit Suisse.</p><p><a href="https://icapital.com/">iCapital</a>, as the leading platform that is responsible for the majority of individual and advisor-led investment flows into the alts space, has its finger on the pulse of what‚Äôs happening in private markets.</p><p>Eileen and I had a fascinating and lively discussion about how technology innovation, and AI and automation in particular, are revolutionizing alternative investments and how technology can drive growth and operational efficiency.</p><p>We covered:</p><ul><li><p>How and why alternatives distribution has evolved.</p></li><li><p>The importance of meeting clients where they are.</p></li><li><p>The evolution of wealth channel strategies.</p></li><li><p>How much does structure matter?</p></li><li><p>When and why Eileen saw registered funds as a major driver of the future growth of private markets well before they became mainstream.</p></li><li><p>The impact of registered and evergreen funds on operations and fund administration.</p></li><li><p>Where will the biggest efficiencies come from in the automation of post-investment processes?</p></li><li><p>How AI and automation will enhance operational efficiency?</p></li></ul><div><hr></div><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png" width="1100" height="220" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:220,&quot;width&quot;:1100,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:60754,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption"><strong>Wanna be featured on eu.vc? Learn how <a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/submit-your-contribution-to-unfiltered">here.</a></strong></figcaption></figure></div></body></html>	How AI and automation are revolutionizing alternative investments and driving growth and operational efficiency.	2024-10-11 10:48:15	2024-10-14 08:19:49.564	2024-10-14 09:32:21.742	{vc,ai}	https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff02ab068-dbee-4fcf-9985-55115dd9221e_1920x1080.jpeg	anon	monthly-alt-pulse-ep-12-taking
143	https://www.eu.vc/p/the-aec-tech-internet-index-by-foundamental	The AEC-Tech Internet Index by Foundamental	by Patric Hellermann, General Partner at Foundamental. | Originally published on Foundamental.	<html><head></head><body><p>Guest post by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/aecvc/">Patric Hellermann</a>, General Partner at <a href="https://www.foundamental.com/">Foundamental</a>. | Originally published on <a href="https://www.foundamental.com/perspectives/internetindex">Foundamental</a>.</p><div><hr></div><p>The largest web traffic and trends analysis for ventures in architecture, engineering, and construction (AEC) technology ever done worldwide. Contains hundreds of the most-funded AEC-Tech startups and scale-ups. </p><p>The index is published monthly, and you can see a preview below. For the complete and updated version of the index, please <a href="https://www.foundamental.com/perspectives/internetindex">read the full version on Foundamental blog</a>.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7548ac34-1ce3-4072-b771-0f441ba87359_800x533.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7548ac34-1ce3-4072-b771-0f441ba87359_800x533.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7548ac34-1ce3-4072-b771-0f441ba87359_800x533.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7548ac34-1ce3-4072-b771-0f441ba87359_800x533.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7548ac34-1ce3-4072-b771-0f441ba87359_800x533.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7548ac34-1ce3-4072-b771-0f441ba87359_800x533.png" width="800" height="533" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7548ac34-1ce3-4072-b771-0f441ba87359_800x533.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:533,&quot;width&quot;:800,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:21907,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:null,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7548ac34-1ce3-4072-b771-0f441ba87359_800x533.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7548ac34-1ce3-4072-b771-0f441ba87359_800x533.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7548ac34-1ce3-4072-b771-0f441ba87359_800x533.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7548ac34-1ce3-4072-b771-0f441ba87359_800x533.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><h4><strong>The AEC-Tech Internet Index:&nbsp;What It Does</strong></h4><p>We use data to shine light on AEC-Technology-related trends we focus on. Here, our data is objective internet traffic for hundreds of startups and scale-ups in architecture, engineering and construction (AEC) technology. Internet traffic gives us non-arbitrary, transparent and robust data points we can use to estimate various trends in AEC-Technology and Construction-Tech, eg. how widespread demand, mindshare and even brand is for venture categories and specific companies in AEC-Tech.</p><p>We hope the community takes the ideas, builds on them, makes them better. We ignore arbitrary 'best-of' lists and 'market maps' propagated by venture pundits.</p><div><hr></div><h3><strong>Risers of the Month</strong></h3><p><em>As a monthly summary, the following charts show the 10 fastest rising AEC ventures in web traffic in the last month, and the most consistently growing AEC ventures over the past 12 months.</em></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff17e33dd-28cd-436a-bd52-88d50fc662db_969x729.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff17e33dd-28cd-436a-bd52-88d50fc662db_969x729.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff17e33dd-28cd-436a-bd52-88d50fc662db_969x729.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff17e33dd-28cd-436a-bd52-88d50fc662db_969x729.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff17e33dd-28cd-436a-bd52-88d50fc662db_969x729.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff17e33dd-28cd-436a-bd52-88d50fc662db_969x729.png" width="969" height="729" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f17e33dd-28cd-436a-bd52-88d50fc662db_969x729.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:729,&quot;width&quot;:969,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:77446,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff17e33dd-28cd-436a-bd52-88d50fc662db_969x729.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff17e33dd-28cd-436a-bd52-88d50fc662db_969x729.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff17e33dd-28cd-436a-bd52-88d50fc662db_969x729.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff17e33dd-28cd-436a-bd52-88d50fc662db_969x729.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><div><hr></div><h3><strong>Category Trends</strong></h3><p><em>For each of our AEC-Tech categories, the following charts identify venture Stars and Dogs in terms of their absolute web traffic scale in the last month mapped against their average monthly growth rate in web traffic.</em></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2faf621a-1662-4051-be26-0e905b24d07a_954x682.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2faf621a-1662-4051-be26-0e905b24d07a_954x682.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2faf621a-1662-4051-be26-0e905b24d07a_954x682.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2faf621a-1662-4051-be26-0e905b24d07a_954x682.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2faf621a-1662-4051-be26-0e905b24d07a_954x682.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2faf621a-1662-4051-be26-0e905b24d07a_954x682.png" width="954" height="682" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2faf621a-1662-4051-be26-0e905b24d07a_954x682.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:682,&quot;width&quot;:954,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:114576,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2faf621a-1662-4051-be26-0e905b24d07a_954x682.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2faf621a-1662-4051-be26-0e905b24d07a_954x682.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2faf621a-1662-4051-be26-0e905b24d07a_954x682.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2faf621a-1662-4051-be26-0e905b24d07a_954x682.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><div><hr></div><h3><strong>Venture Trends</strong></h3><p><em>For each of our AEC-Tech categories, the following charts identify the trending web traffic per AEC venture from today, over the last 6 months and over the last 12 months.</em></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42f3f7ff-3b83-4b62-a634-801173281745_944x710.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42f3f7ff-3b83-4b62-a634-801173281745_944x710.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42f3f7ff-3b83-4b62-a634-801173281745_944x710.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42f3f7ff-3b83-4b62-a634-801173281745_944x710.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42f3f7ff-3b83-4b62-a634-801173281745_944x710.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42f3f7ff-3b83-4b62-a634-801173281745_944x710.png" width="944" height="710" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/42f3f7ff-3b83-4b62-a634-801173281745_944x710.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:710,&quot;width&quot;:944,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:81940,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42f3f7ff-3b83-4b62-a634-801173281745_944x710.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42f3f7ff-3b83-4b62-a634-801173281745_944x710.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42f3f7ff-3b83-4b62-a634-801173281745_944x710.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F42f3f7ff-3b83-4b62-a634-801173281745_944x710.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><div><hr></div><h3><strong>Mindshare Winners</strong></h3><p><em>For each of our AEC-Tech categories, the following charts identify the share of web traffic per AEC venture in its category.</em></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48ce1df1-b9a9-49fc-8b59-8a0c3b3ceaa5_979x716.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48ce1df1-b9a9-49fc-8b59-8a0c3b3ceaa5_979x716.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48ce1df1-b9a9-49fc-8b59-8a0c3b3ceaa5_979x716.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48ce1df1-b9a9-49fc-8b59-8a0c3b3ceaa5_979x716.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48ce1df1-b9a9-49fc-8b59-8a0c3b3ceaa5_979x716.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48ce1df1-b9a9-49fc-8b59-8a0c3b3ceaa5_979x716.png" width="979" height="716" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/48ce1df1-b9a9-49fc-8b59-8a0c3b3ceaa5_979x716.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:716,&quot;width&quot;:979,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:89056,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48ce1df1-b9a9-49fc-8b59-8a0c3b3ceaa5_979x716.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48ce1df1-b9a9-49fc-8b59-8a0c3b3ceaa5_979x716.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48ce1df1-b9a9-49fc-8b59-8a0c3b3ceaa5_979x716.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48ce1df1-b9a9-49fc-8b59-8a0c3b3ceaa5_979x716.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><div><hr></div><h3><strong>Previous Editions: Archive</strong></h3><p>Preserved for posterity, you can access all previous Editions from past months and years of the AEC-Tech Internet Index here:</p><p><a href="https://foundamental.com/InternetIndex/archive">foundamental.com/InternetIndex/archive</a></p><div><hr></div><h3><strong>Methodology</strong></h3><p><strong>Scope</strong>: Foundamental's AEC-Tech Internet Index includes AEC-Tech startups and scale-ups across the globe from North America, Asia (exc. China), Oceania, Europe, Africa and Latin America. founded in 2010 or after, who raised at least a publicly-known total of $25 Million in equity funding. and who did not exit or deadpool before 2019. The Index excludes ventures that are predominantly prop-tech, building operations or logistics-only, or those that have a massive share of their online traffic/visits through an app (instead of website). If the venture is direct-to-consumer (D2C) in AEC, it must show service-components to be considered in scope - eg. Houzz is not in scope for this reason.</p><p><strong>Sources</strong>: The primary data source for the AEC-Tech Internet Index is un-altered Semrush data. The data is updated monthly around the 10th day of each month. Semrush is widely regarded as accurate and reliable in web traffic analysis. While no web traffic analysis is perfectly correct - not even your own instance of Google Analytics - Semrush provides one of the most accurate estimates across the web. The latest version of Foundamental's AEC-Tech Internet Index is always available on <a href="http://foundamental.com/InternetIndex">foundamental.com/InternetIndex</a>, and is also published monthly on Patric Hellermann's Linkedin at <a href="http://linkedin.com/in/aecvc/">linkedin.com/in/aecvc/</a>.</p><div><hr></div><h3><strong>List: AEC-Tech Ventures Contained in this Edition</strong></h3><p>011h.com, adaptive.build, aeroaggna.com, alicetechnologies.com, ambar.tech, andpad.jp, arisinfra.com, assemblyosm.com, assignar.com, billd.com, biomason.com, blockrenovation.com, blokable.com, boringcompany.com, bosscathome.com, boxabl.com, brimstone.com, briq.com, buildcover.com, buildots.com, buildxact.com, builtrobotics.com, capmo.com, carboncure.com, cleanfiber.com, clearstory.build, companycam.com, convex.com, cosuno.com, cove.tools, curbio.com, diamondage3d.com, disperse.io, doxel.ai, dozr.com, dustyrobotics.com, dvele.com, earthgrid.io, ecoworks.tech, enter.de, equipmentshare.com, ergeon.com, factoryos.com, fieldwire.com, finalcad.com, forgeco.com, forteraglobal.com, fyld.ai, getbuilt.com, gobridgit.com, hammertech.com, hero-software.de, higharc.com, homebound.com, hover.to, iconbuild.com, infra.market, inspectpoint.com, jobnimbus.com, join.build, katerra.com, klarx.de, livspace.com, locusview.com, maderenovation.com, manomano.com, materialbank.com, materrup.com, metalbook.co.in, mightybuildings.com, moglix.com, monumental.co, mosaic.us, neustark.com, nexii.com, ofbusiness.com, onsiteiq.io, openspace.ai, permitflow.com, petra.cc, planradar.com, plantprefab.com, powerus.de, pro.com, reconstructinc.com, reibus.com, remihq.com, renorun.com, rhumbix.com, rombit.com, roofr.com, safeai.ai, samara.com, schuettflix.com, screeningeagle.com, sealed.com, sensat.co, siteaware.com, sitetracker.com, snaptrude.com, solidiatech.com, spacemakerai.com, stackct.com, sublime-systems.com, tenderd.com, terraco2.com, trunktools.com, urbint.com, usekojo.com, veev.com, versatile.ai, volue.com, welcomehomes.com, xyzreality.com, zetwerk.com</p><div><hr></div><h3><strong>AEC-Tech Categories Explained</strong></h3><p><strong>Digital General Contractors and Standardized Building Development:</strong> This AEC-Tech category contains ventures that focus on digital platforms to streamline the construction process and standardize building methods for enhanced efficiency and repeatability.</p><p><strong>Financial Services and Embedded Finance:</strong> This AEC-Tech category contains ventures that offer financial solutions, such as project financing, material financing, invoice financing, payment processing, and insurance, specifically tailored for the AEC industry and sometimes integrated into existing workflows.</p><p><strong>Marketplaces:</strong> This AEC-Tech category contains ventures that create tech-enabled platforms connecting buyers and suppliers of construction materials, equipment, labor and services to facilitate and fulfill easier procurement and bidding processes.</p><p><strong>Outcome-as-a-Service (OaaS):</strong> This AEC-Tech category contains ventures that provide performance-based services where clients pay for specific outcomes, such as energy efficiency or building design services, rather than SaaS-only.</p><p><strong>Resource-Efficient Materials and Processes:</strong> This AEC-Tech category contains ventures that develop innovative materials and processes designed to reduce CO2, GHG, waste, and overall enhance sustainability in construction and its supply chains.</p><p><strong>Robotics and (Autonomous) Hardware:</strong> This AEC-Tech category contains ventures that focus on developing robots, autonomous machinery, telematics and other hardware to automate and optimize various construction tasks.</p><p><strong>SaaS - Enterprise and Mid-Market - As-Built &amp; Inspection:</strong> This AEC-Tech category contains ventures that provide software solutions for capturing as-built conditions and managing inspections throughout the construction lifecycle.</p><p><strong>SaaS - Enterprise and Mid-Market - Design &amp; Planning:</strong> This AEC-Tech category contains ventures that develop software platforms to assist in the design and planning phases of construction projects, including CAD, BIM, 3D, 2D and scheduling tools.</p><p><strong>SaaS - Enterprise and Mid-Market - Procurement &amp; Estimation:</strong> This AEC-Tech category contains ventures that offer software to streamline the procurement process and improve cost estimation accuracy for large and mid-sized construction firms.</p><p><strong>SaaS - Enterprise and Mid-Market - Workflows &amp; Resources:</strong> This AEC-Tech category contains ventures that provide software solutions aimed at enhancing project management, resource allocation, and workflow management across the construction industry.</p><p><strong>SaaS - Small Businesses and Freelancers:</strong> This AEC-Tech category contains ventures that develop software tools specifically tailored to the needs of small construction businesses and independent contractors, with a focus on modularity, ease of use and often a deep verticalization.</p><div><hr></div><h3><strong>About Foundamental</strong></h3><p>We here at <a href="https://www.foundamental.com/">Foundamental</a> are the largest global venture investor for AEC-Technology. We currently manage $250M+ in venture capital and we invest in AEC-Technology, including Construction-Tech, since 2019, currently from our third fund. We invest globally across US, APAC, EU.</p><p>As on early backer of AEC category creating ventures such as eg. <a href="https://infra.market/">InfraMarket</a>, <a href="https://snaptrude.com/">Snaptrude</a>, <a href="https://rayon.design/">Rayon</a>, <a href="https://www.monumental.co/">Monumental</a>, <a href="https://enter.de/">Enter</a>, <a href="https://www.mightybuildings.com/">Mighty Buildings</a>, <a href="https://www.safeai.ai/">SafeAI</a>, <a href="https://welcomehomes.com/">Welcome</a>, <a href="https://www.permitflow.com/">Permitflow</a>, <a href="https://www.011h.com/">011h</a> or <a href="https://graneet.com/">Graneet</a>, we have seen our share of trends, categories and data across the AEC&nbsp;startup and technology landscape. We use our global investor perspective to shine light on technology-related trends in the AEC-Tech Internet Index.</p><div><hr></div><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png" width="1100" height="220" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/c2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:220,&quot;width&quot;:1100,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:60754,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" title="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption"><strong>Wanna be featured on eu.vc? Learn how <a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/submit-your-contribution-to-unfiltered">here.</a></strong></figcaption></figure></div></body></html>	Comprehensive data and analysis on the largest web traffic and trends for ventures in architecture, engineering, and construction (AEC) technology.	2024-10-11 14:22:58	2024-10-14 08:19:44.426	2024-10-14 09:20:44.198	{vc}	https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7548ac34-1ce3-4072-b771-0f441ba87359_800x533.png	anon	the-aec-tech-internet-index-by
142	https://www.eu.vc/p/maternity-in-venture-capital-7-in	Maternity in Venture Capital: 7 in 10 Women Concerned About the Return to Work	by Sophie Winwood, co-founder & CEO of WVC:E.	<html><head></head><body><p>Guest post by <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sophie-winwood-92526241/">Sophie Winwood</a>, co-founder &amp; CEO of <a href="https://www.wvce.tech/">WVC:E</a>. </p><div><hr></div><p><strong>Key highlights from the report:</strong></p><ul><li><p>A new report from WVC:E shares the untold stories of mothers in venture capital.&nbsp;</p></li><li><p>120 women in VC from almost 20 countries and funds ranging from less than ‚Ç¨50M to upwards of ‚Ç¨500M were surveyed for the report - 80 per cent of whom are already mothers.</p></li><li><p>Respondents' top three main concerns were career progression, the long-term sustainability of working in VC as a parent and establishing boundaries around work.&nbsp;</p></li><li><p>84 per cent of women surveyed shared that parental leave, both time off and the level of pay, was a concern.</p></li></ul><div><hr></div><p><strong>London, UK. 10th October 2024: </strong><a href="https://www.wvce.tech/">WVC:E</a> has shared a critical report and survey results into motherhood and venture capital. <em>‚Äò<a href="https://www.wvce.tech/maternityreport24">Investing in Women: The Untold Stories of Mothers in VC</a>‚Äô</em> has gathered insights and data from women across European venture capital, analysed parental leave and pay policies across Europe, and interviewed 20 female VCs to present the challenges of navigating VC as a mother.&nbsp;</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2 is-viewable-imag" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F174e0deb-cc1a-4c1a-99fb-b0050578139f_603x868.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F174e0deb-cc1a-4c1a-99fb-b0050578139f_603x868.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F174e0deb-cc1a-4c1a-99fb-b0050578139f_603x868.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F174e0deb-cc1a-4c1a-99fb-b0050578139f_603x868.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F174e0deb-cc1a-4c1a-99fb-b0050578139f_603x868.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F174e0deb-cc1a-4c1a-99fb-b0050578139f_603x868.png" width="603" height="868" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/174e0deb-cc1a-4c1a-99fb-b0050578139f_603x868.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:868,&quot;width&quot;:603,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:357082,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F174e0deb-cc1a-4c1a-99fb-b0050578139f_603x868.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F174e0deb-cc1a-4c1a-99fb-b0050578139f_603x868.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F174e0deb-cc1a-4c1a-99fb-b0050578139f_603x868.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F174e0deb-cc1a-4c1a-99fb-b0050578139f_603x868.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.wvce.tech/maternityreport24&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Read the report here&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.wvce.tech/maternityreport24"><span>Read the report here</span></a></p><p>Data from 120 respondents from 20 European countries and various fund sizes has revealed the following.</p><ul><li><p>Over two-thirds (71 per cent) of women planning on having children or more children were concerned about returning to work in venture capital, and one in five respondents (20 per cent) were very concerned.&nbsp;</p></li><li><p>Almost 80 per cent of respondents felt there was room for improvement in their return to work process, and just over one in three (38 per cent) said there was considerable room for improvement.</p></li><li><p>The top three concerns shared by respondents were career progression/promotion opportunities (32 per cent), the long-term sustainability of working in VC and parenting (25 per cent), and establishing boundaries, e.g., evening events (23 per cent).</p></li><li><p>84 per cent of respondents were concerned about parental leave (the amount of time off or the pay level).&nbsp;</p></li></ul><p>The venture capital industry remains male-dominated despite relatively rapid progress in recent decades. Women comprise 16 per cent of European General Partners, and women comprise only a third of investing teams. In the UK, there has been no change in the gender composition of teams since 2019, with female representation flat at 30 per cent.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Sophie Winwood, CEO of WVC:E, said: </strong></p><div class="pullquote"><p>‚ÄúThe findings in this report shine a light on the unique challenges women face in venture capital, especially when balancing motherhood with the demands of the industry. </p><p>Our goal is not to place blame but to foster understanding and inspire meaningful change. By sharing these experiences, we hope to offer valuable insights, spark important conversations, and drive action across the wider ecosystem ‚Äî in workplaces, homes, and communities. </p><p>It's time to rethink how we support women and build an environment where they can thrive without choosing between career and family.‚Äù</p></div><p><strong>Ruth Foxe Blader, GP of Foxe Capital and Chair of WVC:E, said:</strong></p><div class="pullquote"><p>‚ÄúMaternity and early childcare policy is critical infrastructure needed to rectify employment and pay inequity. But it‚Äôs totally taboo!&nbsp; </p><p>The social dimension is almost more important than the statutory. This report talks about it honestly and all of its complexity.‚Äù</p></div><p><strong>Check Warner, co-founding Partner Ada Ventures and co-founder of Diversity VC, said:</strong></p><div class="pullquote"><p>‚ÄúThe concerning stats in this report should be a wake-up call for the VC industry where parents, particularly women, have been massively let down. Unfortunately, the findings in this report chime with the stories of numerous women who have children when working in VC and have felt completely unsupported by the funds they work for. This is a big missed opportunity, as VC should be compatible with having a family. </p><p>If we as an industry don‚Äôt fix this, we will miss out on the best talent and, therefore, the best returns for investors.‚Äù&nbsp;</p></div><p>The report explores women‚Äôs concerns around parental leave and the differences between men's and women‚Äôs leave, returning to work and setting boundaries regarding policies and practices. It highlights some of these challenges' impacts and offers practical tips on navigating them. The report concludes with recommendations for partners, colleagues, General Partners and the community to improve the status quo for women, men and the industry overall.&nbsp;</p><div><hr></div><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A