-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fc2e93607-5191-4afb-b94b-51d0b094363e_1100x220.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div></div></div></a><figcaption class="image-caption"><strong>Wanna be featured on eu.vc? Learn how <a href="https://www.eu.vc/p/submit-your-contribution-to-unfiltered">here.</a></strong></figcaption></figure></div></body></html>	Untold stories of mothers in venture capital, highlighting their top concerns around career progression, work-life balance, and parental leave policies.	2024-10-12 06:30:59	2024-10-14 08:19:43.355	2024-10-14 09:20:44.198	{vc}	https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F174e0deb-cc1a-4c1a-99fb-b0050578139f_603x868.png	anon	maternity-in-venture-capital-7
