struction and Portfolio Construction &amp; Decomposition,</p><p>‚ÄãLed by Marc Penkala, Co-Founding Partner of ƒÅltitude and advisor to multiple European Family offices and VCs, this masterclass will be delivered in a small-group setting with just 15 seats available, providing a rich opportunity to discuss, exchange perspectives and do hands-on work with the provided material and resources.</p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.eu.vc/publish/post/149815574?back=%2Fpublish%2Fposts%2Fscheduled#:~:text=Join%20the%20masetrclass%20here&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Join the masterclass here&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;button-wrapper&quot;}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary button-wrapper" href="https://www.eu.vc/publish/post/149815574?back=%2Fpublish%2Fposts%2Fscheduled#:~:text=Join%20the%20masetrclass%20here"><span>Join the masterclass here</span></a></p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F0ec2817e-7d9e-456b-8456-0ccf22a1726c_700x40.webp 