x425.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05819799-1f7b-45d3-bf50-c5d53d96443f_347x425.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05819799-1f7b-45d3-bf50-c5d53d96443f_347x425.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05819799-1f7b-45d3-bf50-c5d53d96443f_347x425.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05819799-1f7b-45d3-bf50-c5d53d96443f_347x425.png" width="481" height="589.1210374639769" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/05819799-1f7b-45d3-bf50-c5d53d96443f_347x425.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:425,&quot;width&quot;:347,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:481,&quot;bytes&quot;:44805,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05819799-1f7b-45d3-bf50-c5d53d96443f_347x425.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05819799-1f7b-45d3-bf50-c5d53d96443f_347x425.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05819799-1f7b-45d3-bf50-c5d53d96443f_347x425.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F05819799-1f7b-45d3-bf50-c5d53d96443f_347x425.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></a></figure></div><p>If you see these in your feed you have no clue what these companies do. They need you to be SO impressed by their investors or branding that you go read the rest of the announcement.</p><p>The second one doesn‚Äôt even have a thread below it, just a link to a press article that I‚Äôd bet less than 1% of the people who saw it clicked (and fewer read in full).</p><p>The third one‚Äôs link gives a high-level explanation in the description text for the link that‚Äôs included, but that‚Äôs not a good solution either because including links in the first post of a thread makes the post less likely to show up in people‚Äôs feeds.</p><p>My point:</p><p>You have a split second to alert people to who you are and what you do, on a post that will get 10x or 100x more attention than your average post ‚Äî so say what you do.</p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://thefoundingjourney.substack.com/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://thefoundingjourney.substack.com/subscribe?"><span>Subscribe now</span></a></p><div><hr></div><h2>üí°<strong> How I Can Help</strong></h2><h3><strong>Growth</strong></h3><p><a href="https://go.houck.news/megaphone">Grow your audience + generate leads</a> with my growth service.</p><h3><strong>Fundraising</strong></h3><p><a href="https://go.houck.news/fundraise">Share your round</a> with hundreds of investors in my personal network.</p><h3><strong>Content Creation</strong></h3><p>Let my team and I <a href="https://s665g04yp0s.typeform.com/to/rOXjvxHU">ghostwrite</a> for your newsletter, X, or LinkedIn.</p><h3><strong>Advising</strong></h3><p><a href="https://go.houck.news/advising">I‚Äôll help solve</a> a specific challenge you‚Äôre facing with your startup.</p><p>üöÄ Advertise in my newsletter to <a href="https://go.houck.news/partner">get in front of 60,000+ founders</a>.</p></body></html>	Fundraising announcement is crucial but requires strategic planning. Timing, attention-driving, platform selection, and content are key factors. The most common mistake is not clearly explaining the company's business. Effective announcements can be trajectory-changing.	2024-10-05 11:19:54	2024-10-14 08:16:29.214	2024-10-14 09:20:44.198	{vc}	https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2d52fd0a-42d5-43e7-a9d0-b216b5c9d09a_1456x1048.png	Michael Houck	how-to-announce-your
